-- Reliance Communications May Sell Globalcom Stake to Raise Cash, Line Says
-- Anil Varma
-- 2010-06-17T02:03:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/reliance-communications-may-sell-globalcom-stake-to-raise-cash-line-says.html

          
          
             Reliance Communications Ltd. is
considering raising cash by selling as much as 26 percent of its
Reliance Globalcom unit, which owns a private undersea cable
system, the Hindu BusinessLine reported, without saying where it
got the information. The sale may fetch as much as $500 million,
according to the report.  
